    "accordion_K3YKGe": {
      "type": "accordion",
      "blocks": {
        "accordion_pane_m6HGAA": {
          "type": "accordion_pane",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Does the white one piece swimsuit get transparent when wet?",
            "content": "<p>We line all our white one piece swimsuits with a beige econyl sustainable fabric, to prevent them from becoming transparent.</p>"
          }
        },
        "accordion_pane_zwBQPA": {
          "type": "accordion_pane",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Are black one piece swimsuits flattering?",
            "content": "<p>Black one piece swimsuits are known for there slimming properties. The dark colour creates an illusion of a more streamlined silhouette by minimising the appearance of bulges and creating a sleeker overall look.</p><p></p>"
          }
        },
        "accordion_pane_Py7J3k": {
          "type": "accordion_pane",
          "settings": {
            "title": "How does the low back design enhance the look of the swimsuit?",
            "content": "<p>The low back design of our black one-piece swimwear adds a touch of elegance and allure to the overall look. It creates a flattering silhouette while showcasing just the right amount of skin, making it both chic and sophisticated.</p>"
          }
        },
        "accordion_pane_ArMU9p": {
          "type": "accordion_pane",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Can I wear this swimsuit for both lounging and swimming?",
            "content": "<p>Absolutely! Our black one-piece swimwear with a low back is versatile enough to be worn for lounging by the pool or beach as well as for swimming. The high-quality materials and secure fit provide both comfort and functionality, allowing you to enjoy any water activity with confidence.</p>"
          }
        },
        "accordion_pane_QVTBMM": {
          "type": "accordion_pane",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Is the low back design supportive enough for all-day wear?",
            "content": "<p>Absolutely! Despite its elegant low back design, our black one-piece swimsuit offers ample support and comfort for extended wear. The carefully engineered construction ensures a secure and flattering fit, allowing you to move with confidence.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
